* A2: Clague Garden Estate
* B1: Belvedere Garden, Cable TV Tower
* B2: Station Carpark
* C1: Waterfront Walkway
* C2: OP Mall
* C3: Parc City
* C4: OP Mall
* C5: Waterfront Walkway 
* D: Tsuen Wan Pier 
* E1: Tsuen Wan West Station Public Transport Interchange
* E2: Hoi Kwai Road
